name: NIKHILSTATECAPITALS
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nikhil state capitals
des:
Say "Alexa, Open Nikhil State Capitals" to open the skill.
Next, say "Alexa, I want to find the capital of [your state here]" or just say "Alexa, [your state here]"
Alexa will tell the capital of that state you pick!
After it tells you, you can keep on continuing by saying "Alexa, I want to find the capital of [your state here]" or "Alexa, [your state here]"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
